node.text:
Enjoying our dinner tonight with fresh cod from @lyhseafood The cod is so silky n literally melts in the mouth. Simply umami .

We also have stir fry broccoli n Mapo Tofu which is so good with hot steamed rice .

@lyhseafood has a wide range of fresh seafood. Free delivery with every $65 n above. To order pls contact them @97309931 or order from Instagram or Facebook .
